info.author: Developers
info.description:
### Create a source distribution:

Run ```python setup.py sdist``` inside the project directory.

### Install twine:

```pip install twine```

### Upload package to pypi:

```twine upload dist/*```

### Install dependencies

```sh
pip install -t darwin/libs -r requirements.txt && rm -rf darwin/libs/*.dist-info
```
